  "text": "The INSIGHT-preAD study includes 318 cognitively normal Caucasian individuals, recruited from the community in the wider Paris area, France, aged 70 to 85 years, with SMC. The status of SMC is confirmed as follows: (1) participants gave an affirmative answer (\"yes\") to both questions: \"Are you complaining about your memory?\" and \"Is it a regular complaint that has lasted now more than 6 months?\"; (2) participants presented intact cognitive functions based on Mini-Mental State Examination score [CITATION_1] , Clinical Dementia Rating scale 5 0, and Free and Cued Selective Rating Test (total recall score 41).",
